    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the seven assessed factors demonstrate adequate coverage for the intended submission stage, and the Monte Carlo UQ results provide sufficient uncertainty characterisation for regulatory review. The intermediate hemolysis correlation result, which is described as derived from prior experimental work, was treated by the team as implicitly grounded in published literature and therefore not flagged as requiring explicit provenance linkage. This acceptance does not reflect resolution of all factor gaps; six factors remain not-assessed and the decision is provisional pending further validation activities.",
